    "client_msg_id": "de4cd5b8-7f66-4ac6-9595-86452c288334",
    "text": "Let me add though that many concrete ideas from this presentation look rather dubious to me. For example \"publish first - worry about quality later\", with the \"webs of trust\". Upfront trust doesn't work for complex subject. Even the most careful scientists make mistakes. You can never say \"I trust author X\". Trust can only be derived from expert judgement on a precise statement.",
